Hanna R. Hall https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hanna_R._Hall 0 Hanna Rose Hall (born July 9, 1984) is an American actress. She made her film debut in Forrest Gump (1994), and later appeared in Sofia Coppola's The Virgin Suicides (1999) and Rob Zombie's Halloween (2007).
